reviews.review_text:
Solid show - Excellent recording Lot of great sources for this show but Chris Hecht's is my favorite. Captures everything just the way I want it. Warm and full with clean vocals and instrument separation.

The 4 stars are for the show (barely over two hours with a 51 minute first set), otherwise this is a Grade-A pull.

Deal is smokin'. Bucket seems to have been cut off at the end. Great China Rider, weird experimental PITB, cool Space & Spanish Jam, a lovely Stella / GDTRFB pairing to close out this jawn with a Brokedown encore to send the good folks home.
